<br>
In the above chart, we would see that the most obvious choice for Mana Preservation would be Complete Healing.  But, don't let this data make your decision alone.  You must also look at the speed factor.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
HC / (CT + RT +DU) = Hps (Heal casted divided by Casting time plus Recast time plus Duration = Heal per Second<br>
<br>
A larger number, would mean more healing per second (when casting continuassly).<br>
<br>
<br>
